v1.2.1 (2026.7.13) — Fourth-pass refinement (round-4 cleanup — dead-code purge):
  - Deleted MessageBus.java (AGPL v3): JS side had only a console.log stub and no
    dispatch() callers; the entire Java→JS event-bus was dead code.
  - Deleted UciProtocolHandler.java (GPL v3): its latch-based setOptionAndWait /
    waitForBestmove / waitForUciOk were never used — StockfishNative runs its own
    inline reader loop with its own readyOkLatchHolder / uciOkLatchHolder. Only
    resetHandshakeState() was called (defensively, in cleanup) and even that did
    nothing useful because the latches were never set on this class.
  - Deleted EngineConfigManager.java (GPL v3): the class was instantiated in the
    StockfishNative constructor but no method on the instance was ever called —
    only the MIN_SKILL_LEVEL / MAX_SKILL_LEVEL constants were referenced from
    EngineConfigHelper. Inlined those two constants (0, 20) and removed the class.
  - Slimmed EngineHealthMonitor.java (GPL v3, 208 → 85 lines): removed the
    heartbeat thread, zombie-detection timeouts, and RecoveryCallback interface.
    These duplicated the inline equivalents in StockfishNative and could diverge.
    The class is now a pure state holder for lastResponseTime + autoRecoveryCount
    (the only two pieces of state StockfishNative reads through it).
  - Slimmed EngineProcessManager.java (GPL v3, 489 → 111 lines): removed
    resolveEngineBinary / extractEngineFromApk / extractEngineFromAssets /
    startProcess / initStreams / cleanupResources / isElfFile / process getters
    and setters — all dead code, since StockfishNative keeps its own inline
    copies with direct field access. Only makeExecutable(File) remains, called
    from StockfishNative.makeExecutable for its multi-strategy chmod fallback.
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3): removed _engineConfigManager / _uciProtocolHandler
    / _messageBus fields and their constructor instantiations; removed
    getMessageBus() / _emitLifecycleEvent() / _escapeJsonString() helpers;
    removed 3 _emitLifecycleEvent call sites (engine-ready / engine-error /
    engine-restarting); removed _uciProtocolHandler.resetHandshakeState() call
    in cleanup. EngineHealthMonitor now constructed with no-arg constructor
    (RecoveryCallback wiring removed). EngineProcessManager now constructed
    with ChmodProvider only (Context arg removed). Fixed inline
    extractEngineFromApk ZipEntry.getSize() == -1 divide-by-zero (previously
    only fixed in the now-deleted EngineProcessManager.extractEngineFromApk copy).
  - EngineConfigHelper.java (GPL v3): setEngineSkillLevel now uses inline 0/20
    constants instead of EngineConfigManager.MIN/MAX_SKILL_LEVEL.
  - MainActivity.java (AGPL v3): removed MessageBus JS-interface registration
    (both initial and rebuild paths).
  - No new Java files.


v1.2.1 (2026.7.13) — Second-pass refinement (hardening + bug fix):
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3): P0 TOCTOU race on _discardingPonderBestmove
    fixed (stopAndWaitForBestmove + reader-thread latch-capture path now clear
    the discard flag). P1 Chess960 re-apply symmetry (now applies both true AND
    false based on _pendingChess960). P1 eval-mode option leak fix
    (engineStop now calls restoreGameplayOptions when interrupting STATE_EVAL).
    P1 sendSetOptionAndWait value newline hardening (matches
    UciProtocolHandler.setOptionAndWait). P1 _restartInProgress stale-detection
    (resets after 30s of being stuck). P1 engine-thread-death detection via
    markEngineThreadDead/clearEngineThreadDeadFlag + heartbeat Check 0.
  - JsBridgeGateway.java (GPL v3): P1 isPathInSandbox now requires trailing
    File.separator before startsWith (closes theoretical directory-traversal).
  - SafPickerHelper.java (GPL v3): P1 removed takePersistableWritePermission /
    takePersistableReadPermission — one-shot import/export no longer consumes
    SAF 512-grant cap.
  - StatsActivity.java (AGPL v3): P1 onDestroy now calls webView.stopLoading()
    first (prevents SIGSEGV on HyperOS 3/MIUI). P1 removed
    takePersistableUriPermission for PGN import.
  - ChessApp.java (AGPL v3): P1 SF-* thread UncaughtExceptionHandler now calls
    StockfishNative.markEngineThreadDead to trigger heartbeat recovery.
  - HapticHelper.java (GPL v3): P2 perform() now respects system
    HAPTIC_FEEDBACK_ENABLED setting (matches StatsActivity.performHaptic).
    [v1.2.1 round-10 NOTE: HapticHelper.java has been REMOVED — see the
    round-10 entry below. The historical round-2 entry is preserved for
    audit trail.]
  - EngineProcessManager.java (GPL v3): P2 extractEngineFromApk guards against
    ZipEntry.getSize() == -1 (divide-by-zero / negative progress percentage).
  - No new Java files.

