v1.2.0 Phase 73-75 (2026.7.11):
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3): ENGINE_VERSION "v1.1.2" → "v1.2.0".
      God Module split: extracted 6 manager classes.
      SonarCloud bug fixes: InterruptedException re-interrupt, delete()/renameTo()
      return value checks, AtomicInteger for thread-safe counters.
  - EngineProcessManager.java (GPL v3, NEW): Engine process lifecycle management.
      Extracted from StockfishNative.java. Handles start/stop/restart, binary
      extraction, chmod/renice, ELF verification, stream initialization.
  - UciProtocolHandler.java (GPL v3, NEW): UCI protocol command handling.
      Extracted from StockfishNative.java. Handles command sending, response
      parsing (uciok/readyok/bestmove), setoption synchronization.
  - EngineConfigManager.java (GPL v3, NEW): Engine configuration management.
      Extracted from StockfishNative.java. Handles settings persistence,
      import/export, range validation, auto-detection.
  - JsBridgeGateway.java (GPL v3, NEW): JS bridge security gateway.
      Extracted from StockfishNative.java. Provides sandbox path validation,
      UCI command whitelisting, input sanitization.
  - PgnCacheManager.java (GPL v3, NEW): PGN cache CRUD operations.
      Extracted from StockfishNative.java. Handles cache directory, file
      read/write/delete/rename, tag file management.
  - EngineHealthMonitor.java (GPL v3, NEW): Engine health monitoring.
      Extracted from StockfishNative.java. Handles heartbeat thread, zombie
      detection, auto-recovery backoff with AtomicInteger counters.
  - MessageBus.java (AGPL v3, NEW Phase 75): JS ↔ Java unified message bus.
      Provides dispatch(action, payload) for JS→Java and emit(event, payload)
      for Java→JS communication.
  - MainActivity.java (AGPL v3): VERSION "v1.1.2" → "v1.2.0".
  - ChessApp.java (AGPL v3): init log "v1.1.2" → "v1.2.0".
  - ChessWebViewClient.java (AGPL v3): Version comment "v1.1.2" → "v1.2.0".


v1.2.0 Phase 73+ (2026.7.11) — Additional helper classes:
  - FileIoHelper.java (GPL v3, NEW): File I/O operations extracted from
      StockfishNative.java. Handles writeTextFile (3-tier fallback: primary→
      app-private→clipboard), readTextFile (with READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE on
      Android 5-9), listFiles (with MediaStore supplement on Android 11+),
      loadAssetAsBase64 (with ".." path-traversal check), getDefaultPaths,
      getExportPath, getParentPath, scanEngines (stub for JS API compat).
      File I/O patterns derived from DroidFish EngineUtil.java.
  - PermissionHelper.java (GPL v3, NEW): Runtime permission checks extracted
      from StockfishNative.java. Handles storage (Android version-aware:
      WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE on 5-9, READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE on 10-12, none on
      13+), notification (POST_NOTIFICATIONS on 13+), and vibrator checks.
      Uses checkSelfPermission() (not checkCallingOrSelfPermission) to avoid
      WebView caller-identity mismatch. Permission patterns derived from
      DroidFish EngineOptionsDialog.java.
  - HapticHelper.java (GPL v3, NEW): Haptic feedback extracted from
      StockfishNative.java. Provides perform(type) with type-specific durations
      (BUTTON_PRESS/PIECE_MOVE/CAPTURE/CHECK/GAME_END/ERROR). Uses
      VibrationEffect.createOneShot on Android 8+, deprecated vibrate(long) on
      Android 7 and below (minSdk=23). Haptic patterns derived from DroidFish
      EngineUtil.java vibration.
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3): @JavascriptInterface methods for file I/O,
      permissions, and vibrator now delegate to the new helper classes,
      reducing StockfishNative from 5,443 to 4,976 lines.

  - SafPickerHelper.java (GPL v3, NEW): SAF file picker extracted from
      StockfishNative.java. Handles:
        - Export: openExportFilePicker (settings TXT), openPGNExportFilePicker (PGN),
          handleExportResult (writes content to user-chosen URI via ContentResolver),
          cancelPendingExport (user dismissed picker).
        - Import: openSystemFilePicker (settings TXT), openPGNFilePicker (PGN),
          handleImportResult (reads file + calls importSettings),
          handlePGNImportResult (reads PGN with 5000-line truncation guard +
          control-character sanitization + JSON-safe encoding).
      SAF patterns derived from DroidFish EngineOptionsDialog.java.
      Request codes (REQUEST_CODE_IMPORT_SETTINGS/EXPORT_SETTINGS/IMPORT_PGN/
      EXPORT_PGN) moved here as constants; StockfishNative re-exports them for
      MainActivity.onActivityResult compatibility.

  - EngineSettingsHelper.java (GPL v3, NEW): Engine settings query/export/import
      extracted from StockfishNative.java. Handles:
        - getEngineInfo(): builds JSON with name/author/path/threads/hash/autoConfig.
        - getEngineSettings(): builds JSON with all configurable params.
        - exportSettings(): exports as TXT key=value format with comment header.
        - exportEngineSettings(): alias for exportSettings (JS API compat).
        - importSettings(txtContent): parses TXT, applies range capping
          (threads ≤ 2×CPU cores, hash ≤ 50% JVM heap, moveOverhead ≤ 1000ms,
          multiPV 1-8, skillLevel 0-20, elo 1-3200), persists to prefs,
          applies to running engine via stopAndWaitForBestmove + applySettings.
          Disables autoConfig when user explicitly imports threads/hash.
        - importEngineSettings(): alias for importSettings (JS API compat).
      Uses Callbacks interface to access StockfishNative engine state.
      Settings patterns derived from DroidFish EngineOptionsDialog.java.

v1.2.0 Phase 81 (2026.7.11) — Engine config helper extraction:
  - EngineConfigHelper.java (GPL v3, NEW): Engine configuration methods extracted
    from StockfishNative.java. Handles:
        - setAutoConfig(enabled): toggle auto-config + trigger hardware detection.
        - detectHardwareAndConfigure(): big.LITTLE-aware Threads/Hash detection
          (reads /proc/cpuinfo, caches big-core count for device lifetime).
        - detectBigCoreCount(): parses /proc/cpuinfo for per-core max frequency,
          counts cores >= 90% of highest freq (when highest > 1.2× median).
        - applySettings(): applies all UCI options in order (Threads/Hash source
          depends on autoConfig; common options applied identically).
        - setEngineThreads/Hash/MoveOverhead/MultiPV/Ponder/ShowWDL/SkillLevel/
          LimitElo/Elo: UCI option setters with range capping (same Phase 71
          limits as EngineSettingsHelper.importSettings).
        - setGameDifficulty(level 1-7): maps to ELO_MAP (moved here from
          StockfishNative — only used by this method). Levels 1-6 enable
          UCI_LimitStrength + set UCI_Elo; level 7 disables LimitStrength.
        - forceFullStrength(): temporary override for eval/hint searches
          (sets Skill Level 20, UCI_LimitStrength false).
        - syncGameDifficulty(level): JS-side sync wrapper with logging.
        - setShowWDL/setLimitStrength/setElo: JS API compat aliases.
    Uses Callbacks interface for field access (setThreadsField etc. update field
    + persist, no UCI command) and engine operations (sendSetOptionAndWait,
    sendUciCommand, engineSupportsOption, notifyEngineInfo, postJsCallback).
    StockfishNative retains thin @JavascriptInterface delegates. StockfishNative:
    4,492→4,245 lines (−247). Helper/manager class count: 12→13 (14 with MessageBus).
